'''"Snow" '''("Сняг") is a [[Bulgaria]]n [[Live action|film]], a co-production with [[Ukraine]], from 2015, directed by Ventsislav Vasilev.
The film premiere was at the XXXIII edition of the [[Golden Rose Film Festival]] in [[Varna]] on 9 October 2015.<ref>{{cite web |language=bg |url=http://www.zlatnaroza.bg/portfolio/сняг/ |website=zlatnaroza.bg |access-date=13 March 2016}}</ref> The film participated at the XXXI Warsaw International Film Festival, which took place in October 2015,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wff.pl/en/aktualnosci/konkurs-midzynarodowy-na-31-wff |title=International Competition at 31st WFF |website=wff.pl |date=23 September 2015 |access-date=13 March 2016}}</ref> and at the XXV festival for Eastern European cinema in Cottbus, Germany in November 2015. During the XIV festival for European cinema Cinedays in Skopje in 2015 it won the "Golden Sun" award for the best Balkan film. It participated at the XX [[Sofia International Film Festival|Sofia International Film Fest]] in March 2016.<ref>{{cite web |language=bg |last=Луканов |first=Йордан |url=http://www.weekendclub.bg/sofiya-film-fest-2016-snyag-na-vencislav-vasilev-otkriva-mezhdunarodniya-konkurs/3/1128/ |title=София Филм Фест 2016: "Сняг" на Венцислав Василев открива Международния конкурс |website=weekendclub.bg |date=12 March 2016 |access-date=13 March 2016}}</ref>
